atlas.about: Metadata on the last processing of the atlas styles api response

debug_changed_names.about: The folder names in Mapbox need to follow a pattern of `atlas_[DataIdentifier]_[OptionalStyleIdentifier]`, otherwise the script will create unexpected results. During processing, we cleanup the names. If any names show up below, those need to be fixed in Mapbox to prevent errors.
